                    <li><Tooltip term="Hidden Order ·õâ">Hidden Order ·õâ</Tooltip>: Help the <Tooltip term="Fate Weaver ·ö®">Fate Weaver</Tooltip> survive. If they win, you win (even if you've been eliminated).</li>
                    <li><Tooltip term="Thread Breaker ·õà">Thread Breaker ·õà</Tooltip>: Defeat the <Tooltip term="Fate Weaver ·ö®">Fate Weaver</Tooltip>, AND at least one <Tooltip term="Thread Breaker ·õà">Thread Breaker</Tooltip> must survive (even if you've been eliminated).</li>
                </ul>

                <SubSectionHeader id="first-turn" title="Your First Turn (Guided Example): Simple Steps to Action!" icon={ScrollText} />
                <p className="mb-6 text-lg">Follow these simplified steps to play your first turn. We'll explain more later!</p>
                <ol className="list-decimal list-inside mb-6 space-y-4 text-lg">
                    <li>
                        <h4 className={`text-xl font-medium mb-2 ${theme === 'dark' ? 'text-indigo-200' : 'text-indigo-700'}`}>Rune Phase (Icon: üé≤):</h4>
