                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <h4 className={`text-xl font-medium mb-2 ${theme === 'dark' ? 'text-indigo-200' : 'text-indigo-700'}`}>Draw Phase (Icon: ‚û°Ô∏èüìú):</h4>
                        <ul className="list-circle list-inside ml-6 space-y-1">
