                    <li>Fate Watcher</li>
                </ul>

                <ul className="list-none mb-6 pl-0 space-y-1 text-lg">
                    <li><strong>Players:</strong> 4-6 (The game adjusts for player count)</li>
                    <li><strong>Setup Time:</strong> ~10-15 minutes after First Standard Game.</li>
